    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with your <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> dried oregano </strong>and the<strong> </strong>juice of <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s] </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong>,<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix to combine – this is your <strong>peri peri sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1625561689883-x200.jpg",
