        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>marinated tofu cubes</strong> and cook for 5-6 min, turning occasionally until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
