        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>peri peri sauce</strong> to the pan with the tofu and cook over a high heat for 2-3 min turning a few times or until the sauce has reduced and the tofu is coated</p><p>Once done, remove from the pan and set aside for later (save the pan!) – this is your <strong>peri peri tofu</strong></p>",
