    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, in a separate small bowl combine the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>tangy</strong> <strong>lemon dressing</strong></p>",
