      "instruction": "<p>Assemble the salad with the <strong>reserved lettuce</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> first, then add the <strong>smoky sweetcorn & beans</strong> and the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>peri peri tofu</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>tangy</strong> <strong>lemon dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
